Yi is not very good unless very ahead vs bad team comps (the typical all carry teams). Recently I tried him botlane - enemy team had 4 tanks; Yi shreds tanks, right? Wrong, you get CCed and bursted in the AOE by base dmgs. Very unreliable champ. Still, we won, but that was because enemy team had Ezrael - which is a dogshit champion that few can actually play and started misplaying lategame.
Irelia, Jax, Fiora and Camille are somewhat similar to Yi. Fiora is maybe the worst in teamfights; aside from being very good in 1v1s, because of her no counterplay R.
The biggest abuser of conqueror is Yasuo that you didn't mention for some reason. He has no cds and spams HARD Q and autos even early game.

